[2026-04-08T21:44:42.462Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QKqd8EYAs2YqQVaszprzud","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# InvoiceFlow - Solution Design Document\n2\t\n3\t> **Version**: 1.0.0  \n4\t> **Last Updated**: December 2024  \n5\t> **Architecture**: NextJS 14 + Supabase + Groq + React-PDF + RevenueCat\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## Table of Contents\n10\t\n11\t1. [Executive Summary](#1-executive-summary)\n12\t2. [System Architecture](#2-system-architecture)\n13\t3. [Technology Stack](#3-technology-stack)\n14\t4. [Database Schema](#4-database-schema)\n15\t5. [Internationalization (i18n)](#5-internationalization-i18n)\n16\t6. [Country-Specific Invoice Requirements](#6-country-specific-invoice-requirements)\n17\t7. [LLM Integration (Groq)](#7-llm-integration-groq)\n18\t8. [PDF Generation (React-PDF)](#8-pdf-generation-react-pdf)\n19\t9. [RevenueCat Paywall Integration](#9-revenuecat-paywall-integration)\n20\t10. [UI/UX Design System](#10-uiux-design-system)\n21\t11. [Automation Features](#11-automation-features)\n22\t12. [API Design](#12-api-design)\n23\t13. [Security & Compliance](#13-security--compliance)\n24\t14. [Deployment & Infrastructure](#14-deployment--infrastructure)\n25\t\n26\t---\n27\t\n28\t## 1. Executive Summary\n29\t\n30\t### Vision\n31\t\n32\tInvoiceFlow is a next-generation invoice management platform designed for minimal user effort and maximum automation. The system leverages AI to extract invoice data, auto-fill forms, and predict user needs while maintaining compliance with international invoicing standards.\n33\t\n34\t### Core Principles\n35\t\n36\t| Principle | Implementation |\n37\t|-----------|----------------|\n38\t| **Zero-friction** | AI auto-extraction, smart defaults, one-click actions |\n39\t| **Minimal UI** | Compact, information-dense layouts with progressive disclosure |\n40\t| **Global-first** | Multi-country support from day one |\n41\t| **Offline-capable** | PWA with local caching |\n42\t| **Cost-efficient** | Free tier viable, predictable scaling costs |\n43\t\n44\t### Target Users\n45\t\n46\t- **Self-employed individuals** (OSVČ in CZ, Freelancers in DE, Sole Traders in UK)\n47\t- **Micro-businesses** (1-10 employees)\n48\t- **Accountants** managing multiple clients\n49\t\n50\t---\n51\t\n52\t## 2. System Architecture\n53\t\n54\t### High-Level Architecture\n55\t\n56\t```\n57\t┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n58\t│                              CLIENT LAYER                                   │\n59\t│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n60\t│  │                    NextJS 14 App Router (PWA)                       │   │\n61\t│  │  ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐  │   │\n62\t│  │  │Dashboard │ │ Inbox    │ │ Editor   │ │ Contacts │ │ Settings │  │   │\n63\t│  │  │ Widget   │ │ (Scan)   │ │ (Create) │ │ (CRM)    │ │ (i18n)   │  │   │\n64\t│  │  └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘  │   │\n65\t│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n66\t└─────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────┘\n67\t                                  │\n68\t┌─────────────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────────┐\n69\t│                              API LAYER                                      │\n70\t│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n71\t│  │                    NextJS API Routes + tRPC                          │   │\n72\t│  │  ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌────────────┐  │   │\n73\t│  │  │ /api/ocr     │ │ /api/invoice │ │ /api/export  │ │ /api/sub   │  │   │\n74\t│  │  │ Groq Vision  │ │ CRUD + Rules │ │ PDF/CSV/XML  │ │ RevenueCat │  │   │\n75\t│  │  └──────┬───────┘ └──────┬───────┘ └──────┬───────┘ └─────┬──────┘  │   │\n76\t│  └─────────┼────────────────┼────────────────┼───────────────┼──────────┘   │\n77\t└────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────┼───────────────┼──────────────┘\n78\t             │                │                │               │\n79\t┌────────────▼────────────────▼────────────────▼───────────────▼──────────────┐\n80\t│                           SERVICE LAYER                                     │\n81\t│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  │\n82\t│  │   Groq AI   │  │            Supabase                 │  │ RevenueCat  │  │\n83\t│  │  ┌───────┐  │  │  ┌──────────┐ ┌────────┐ ┌───────┐  │  │  ┌───────┐  │  │\n84\t│  │  │LLaVA  │  │  │  │PostgreSQL│ │Storage │ │ Auth  │  │  │  │ Subs  │  │  │\n85\t│  │  │Mixtral│  │  │  │ + RLS    │ │(S3)    │ │(OAuth)│  │  │  │ Plans │  │  │\n86\t│  │  └───────┘  │  │  └──────────┘ └────────┘ └───────┘  │  │  └───────┘  │  │\n87\t│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────────────────────────────┘  └─────────────┘  │\n88\t└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n89\t```\n90\t\n91\t### Data Flow: Invoice OCR Processing\n92\t\n93\t```\n94\t┌─────────┐    ┌─────────┐    ┌─────────┐    ┌─────────┐    ┌─────────┐\n95\t│ Upload  │───▶│ Storage │───▶│  Groq   │───▶│ Validate│───▶│  Save   │\n96\t│ Image   │    │ Bucket  │    │  OCR    │    │ + Enrich│    │   DB    │\n97\t└─────────┘    └─────────┘    └─────────┘    └─────────┘    └─────────┘\n98\t     │                             │               │\n99\t     │                             ▼               ▼\n100\t     │                      ┌─────────────────────────┐\n101\t     │                      │  Country Validator      │\n102\t     │                      │  • CZ: ARES API (IČO)   │\n103\t     │                      │  • DE: Handelsregister  │\n104\t     │                      │  • UK: Companies House  │\n105\t     │                      └─────────────────────────┘\n106\t     │\n107\t     ▼\n108\t┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n109\t│              Real-time UI Update                    │\n110\t│  • Skeleton → Confidence bars → Final data          │\n111\t│  • Inline corrections with learning                 │\n112\t└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n113\t```\n114\t\n115\t---\n116\t\n117\t## 3. Technology Stack\n118\t\n119\t### Core Stack\n120\t\n121\t| Layer | Technology | Rationale |\n122\t|-------|------------|-----------|\n123\t| **Framework** | NextJS 14 (App Router) | RSC, streaming, edge runtime |\n124\t| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | RLS, realtime, generous free tier |\n125\t| **Auth** | Supabase Auth | OAuth, magic links, MFA |\n126\t| **Storage** | Supabase Storage | S3-compatible, CDN |\n127\t| **AI/LLM** | Groq (Mixtral/LLaVA) | Fast inference, cost-effective |\n128\t| **PDF** | React-PDF/renderer | React-native PDF generation |\n129\t| **Payments** | RevenueCat | Cross-platform subscription management |\n130\t| **i18n** | next-intl | Type-safe, RSC-compatible |\n131\t| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS + Radix UI | Utility-first, accessible primitives |\n132\t| **State** | Zustand + TanStack Query | Minimal boilerplate, caching |\n133\t| **Validation** | Zod | Runtime type validation |\n134\t\n135\t### Package Dependencies\n136\t\n137\t```json\n138\t{\n139\t  \"dependencies\": {\n140\t    \"next\": \"^14.2.0\",\n141\t    \"@supabase/supabase-js\": \"^2.45.0\",\n142\t    \"@supabase/ssr\": \"^0.5.0\",\n143\t    \"groq-sdk\": \"^0.5.0\",\n144\t    \"@react-pdf/renderer\": \"^3.4.0\",\n145\t    \"purchases-js\": \"^0.10.0\",\n146\t    \"next-intl\": \"^3.20.0\",\n147\t    \"@radix-ui/react-*\": \"latest\",\n148\t    \"tailwindcss\": \"^3.4.0\",\n149\t    \"zustand\": \"^4.5.0\",\n150\t    \"@tanstack/react-query\": \"^5.50.0\",\n151\t    \"zod\": \"^3.23.0\",\n152\t    \"lucide-react\": \"^0.400.0\",\n153\t    \"date-fns\": \"^3.6.0\",\n154\t    \"react-dropzone\": \"^14.2.0\",\n155\t    \"framer-motion\": \"^11.3.0\"\n156\t  }\n157\t}\n158\t```\n159\t\n160\t---\n161\t\n162\t## 4. Database Schema\n163\t\n164\t### Entity Relationship Diagram\n165\t\n166\t```\n167\t┌─────────────────┐       ┌─────────────────┐       ┌─────────────────┐\n168\t│   users         │       │  organizations  │       │   team_members  │\n169\t├─────────────────┤       ├─────────────────┤       ├─────────────────┤\n170\t│ id (PK)         │◄──┐   │ id (PK)         │◄──────│ id (PK)         │\n171\t│ email           │   │   │ owner_id (FK)───┼───────│ org_id (FK)     │\n172\t│ full_name       │   │   │ name            │       │ user_id (FK)────┼───┐\n173\t│ avatar_url      │   │   │ country_code    │       │ role            │   │\n174\t│ locale          │   │   │ tax_id          │       │ invited_at      │   │\n175\t│ created_at      │   │   │ vat_id          │       └─────────────────┘   │\n176\t└─────────────────┘   │   │ entity_type     │                             │\n177\t                      │   │ settings (JSONB)│       ┌─────────────────┐   │\n178\t                      │   │ created_at      │       │  subscriptions  │   │\n179\t                      │   └─────────────────┘       ├─────────────────┤   │\n180\t                      │           │                 │ id (PK)         │   │\n181\t                      │           │                 │ user_id (FK)────┼───┘\n182\t                      │           ▼                 │ rc_customer_id  │\n183\t                      │   ┌─────────────────┐       │ plan_id         │\n184\t                      │   │    contacts     │       │ status          │\n185\t                      │   ├─────────────────┤       │ current_period  │\n186\t                      │   │ id (PK)         │       │ entitlements    │\n187\t                      │   │ org_id (FK)     │       └─────────────────┘\n188\t                      │   │ type (enum)     │\n189\t                      │   │ name            │       ┌─────────────────┐\n190\t                      │   │ country_code    │       │country_configs  │\n191\t    