[2026-04-08T21:44:49.679Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PYw8eaLgEVmbt6B3jAsxbr","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# CLAUDE.md\n2\t\n3\t## Project Overview\n4\t\n5\t**InvoiceFlow** (`auto-invoicer`) — A next-generation invoice management platform for freelancers, micro-businesses, and accountants. AI-powered OCR extraction, multi-country compliance, and one-click PDF generation. Currently in early development with a themed invoice form UI.\n6\t\n7\t## Tech Stack\n8\t\n9\t- **Language**: TypeScript 5\n10\t- **Framework**: Next.js 16.0.6 (App Router)\n11\t- **Runtime**: React 19.2.0\n12\t- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 (PostCSS plugin, `@import \"tailwindcss\"` syntax)\n13\t- **Fonts**: Geist, Geist Mono, Caveat (via `next/font/google`)\n14\t- **Linting**: ESLint 9 flat config (next core-web-vitals + typescript)\n15\t- **Planned integrations**: Supabase (DB/Auth/Storage), Groq AI (OCR/LLM), React-PDF, RevenueCat (payments)\n16\t\n17\t## Common Commands\n18\t\n19\t### Development\n20\t```bash\n21\tnpm run dev      # Start Next.js dev server (localhost:3000)\n22\tnpm run build    # Production build\n23\tnpm run start    # Start production server\n24\tnpm run lint     # ESLint check\n25\t```\n26\t\n27\t### Setup\n28\t```bash\n29\tnpm install      # Install dependencies (node_modules not committed)\n30\t```\n31\t\n32\t## Architecture Overview\n33\t\n34\t```\n35\tsrc/\n36\t  app/\n37\t    page.tsx        — Main invoice form (single-file, client component with theme system)\n38\t    layout.tsx      — Root layout (Geist + Caveat fonts, metadata)\n39\t    globals.css     — Tailwind import + CSS custom properties (light/dark)\n40\t    favicon.ico\n41\tpublic/             — Static SVG assets (file, globe, next, vercel, window)\n42\trequirements/\n43\t  solution.md       — Full solution design document (architecture, DB schema, i18n, etc.)\n44\t```\n45\t\n46\t## Code Conventions\n47\t\n48\t### Naming\n49\t- Components: PascalCase (`InvoiceForm`, `ThemeSwitcher`)\n50\t- Files: kebab-case for configs, PascalCase not yet established for component files\n51\t- Variables: camelCase\n52\t- Theme tokens: camelCase properties in TypeScript interfaces\n53\t\n54\t### Patterns\n55\t- **Theming**: Token-based theme system using React Context (`ThemeContext`) with Tailwind class strings as values\n56\t- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS utility classes, dynamic class composition via template literals\n57\t- **State**: React `useState` + Context (no external state library yet)\n58\t- **Imports**: Absolute imports via `@/*` path alias (maps to `./src/*`)\n59\t\n60\t### Current Themes\n61\t- `minimal-mono` — Ultra-minimal monochrome, font-mono, no shadows\n62\t- `paper-perfect` — Warm paper aesthetic, Caveat handwriting font, rounded cards with shadows\n63\t\n64\t## Important Conventions\n65\t\n66\t- Tailwind v4 uses `@import \"tailwindcss\"` (not `@tailwind` directives)\n67\t- Tailwind v4 uses `@theme inline {}` for custom theme tokens in CSS\n68\t- ESLint uses flat config format (`eslint.config.mjs`)\n69\t- Path alias `@/*` → `./src/*` configured in `tsconfig.json`\n70\t- Dark mode via `prefers-color-scheme` media query in CSS custom properties\n71\t\n72\t## Do NOT\n73\t\n74\t- Do not commit `.env*` files (gitignored)\n75\t- Do not commit `node_modules/` or `.next/`\n76\t- Do not modify `next-env.d.ts` (auto-generated)\n77\t- Do not use Tailwind v3 syntax (`@tailwind base`, `theme()` function, etc.)\n78\t\n[result-id: r14]"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01B24bGzbWozuAkJerWXmjz8","session_id":"3222cf1b-2930-4f4b-a1c0-9f3e8ac0d429","uuid":"cb21d185-6422-43f6-8783-6979f62a4e90","timestamp":"2026-04-08T21:44:49.518Z"}
