uild\nnpm run start    # Run production build\nnpm run lint     # ESLint validation\n```\n\n**CI/CD** (GitHub Actions)\n- Trigger: push to master branch or PR to master\n- Steps: npm ci → npm run lint → npm run build\n\n---\n\n### Project Status & Dependencies\n\n**Stage**: Early Development (Alpha)\n- Core UI infrastructure complete\n- Theme system functional\n- Form layout designed but not wired to backend\n- No backend integrations yet (Supabase, Groq, RevenueCat planned)\n\n**Dependencies**: \n- 3 production deps (next, react, react-dom)\n- 5 devDeps (Tailwind, TypeScript, ESLint, types)\n- Total: ~8 direct dependencies (minimal footprint)\n\n**Node Version**: 20+ (per CI configuration)\n\n---\n\n### Important Notes\n\n1. **Tailwind v4 Syntax**: Uses `@import \"tailwindcss\"` + `@theme inline {}` (not v3's `@tailwind` directives)\n2. **No Backend Yet**: All backend APIs defined in solution.md but not implemented\n3. **Theming is Central**: The entire invoice UI is theme-driven; design changes must account for token system\n4. **Type Safety**: Full TypeScript strict mode enabled\n5. **AI Integration Planned**: Groq LLM will handle OCR, data extraction, and predictions once integrated\n\n---\n\nThis codebase represents a well-structured, early-stage SaaS application for invoice management with a focus on AI automation, multi-country compliance, and user experience through themeable interfaces. The solution design is comprehensive, and the initial implementation establishes a solid foundation for progressive development of planned features."}],"totalDurationMs":65240,"totalTokens":42412,"totalToolUseCount":22,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1023,"cache_read_input_tokens":38163,"output_tokens":3220,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1023},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
